docs.text: Wine-Mono installation: Download this: https://dl.winehq.org/wine/wine-mono/5.1.1/wine-mono-5.1.1-x86.msi In Terminal run wine uninstaller A Window should pop up, click on install and find the MSI you downloaded earlier Congrats, you now have Wine-Mono installed!
